OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FA German man has been found guilty of
OL,8,Fdrugging and raping his unconscious
OL,9,Fwife over several years and sharing
OL,10,Fvideos of the abuse online.
OL,12,FFernando P, a 61-year-old school
OL,13,Fjanitor, was convicted of repeatedly
OL,14,Fassaulting his wife in their home,
OL,15,Fsecretly filming the attacks and
OL,16,Fposting the footage on the internet
OL,17,Fwithout her knowledge.
