OL,7,FHe was sentenced on Friday to eight
OL,8,Fyears and six months in prison
OL,9,Ffollowing a trial in Aachen, western
OL,10,FGermany.
OL,12,FThe court said the man violated "the
OL,13,Fmost intimate sphere of private life
OL,14,Fand of personal rights through image
OL,15,Frecordings in 34 cases, including in
OL,16,Ffour cases in concurrence with
OL,17,Faggravated rape and dangerous bodily
OL,18,Fharm".
