OL,3,CGerman man who drugged, raped and
OL,4,Cfilmed his wife for years jailed for 8
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FThe verdict comes exactly a year after
OL,8,FFrenchman Dominique Pelicot was found
OL,9,Fguilty of aggravated rape.
OL,11,FPelicot had recruited dozens of
OL,12,Fstrangers through an online chatroom
OL,13,Fover nearly a decade to rape and abuse
OL,14,Fhis then-wife, Gisele.
OL,16,FAnother 49 men were also convicted of
OL,17,Frape or sexual assault in that case.
OL,19,FThe Pelicot case shocked France and
OL,20,Fprompted a wider reckoning over gender-
OL,21,Fbased violence and misogyny.
